StarCCM Macro 

Iterate through different grid sizes and export results to home directory 

To use the macro: 
    - load the star.sim file
    - set required physics and stopping criteria (maximum steps)
    - File -> Macro -> Play Macro

To edit or add grid sizes: edit the map at line 22

To change output directory or filename: edit output options on line 204. 
    - Defaults to home directory with filename "data{gridsize}.csv"
